<Content>Clean, comfortable, and in a great location. The Onix Fira is a nice modern choice in central Barcelona. I travel with my computer, and free wireless internet in this hotel was a big bonus. The rooms are bright and spacious, the air-co works well, and the staff are helpful and courteous. 2 main metro lines are just around the corner. Good for families, the (very) small rooftop pool is a plus, as is the nicely appointed breakfast area on the ground floor. We'd return here on our next trip. 
